metadata.name: summer girl
metadata.description:
In this artwork, the girl is portrayed as a carefree spirit, enjoying the warmth of the summer sun. Her white hat shields her eyes from the bright light, casting her face in a soft, warm glow. Her smile is wide and bright, as if she is relishing in the joys of the season.

The summer girl's skin is depicted with a warm, sun-kissed glow that perfectly captures the feeling of a sunny day. The colors of her outfit, with shades of white and light blue, perfectly complement the overall aesthetic of the artwork.

In this portrait of a summer girl with a white hat has captured the essence of the season and the feeling of being carefree and happy.
